            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We gone to sought admission  for my son for 2nd std. They gave  one question paper ( 1 st question paper) and asked my son to write answers. Since all children are on online session for two years, my son had little trouble to do on his own. After the completion, the coordinator came to us and told  like \"your son doesn't know anything, he doesn't have understanding capacity at all.\" So she  suggested us to put our son in 1 st std. How can a school  conclude that the child doesn't have these capabilities. We didn't expert this at all from this institution. My son can read and write fluently.  Such an worst attitude and judgemental.",
          "publisher": {
