            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Excellent school. Friendly and very responsive teachers and management. Neatly organized, safe and tidy premises. Not over crowded classroom strength, which I liked the most as each student gets their own attention from the teachers and the individual identity of the kids is not lost. My kids attended this school for the past few years. I was totally satisfied and happy how they had progressed academically. Best IGCSE school in the kolapakkam area. I had to leave this school as we moved out of the country, but my kids and I still miss this wonderful school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
